      "case_id": "rec-expert-004",
      "question": "What are the top 10 movies to recommend to User 1, factoring in both what similar users enjoyed and whether the movie's genres match their viewing history? Weight peer ratings more heavily than genre overlap.",
      "difficulty": "expert",
      "tags": [
        "match",
